title: [docs] Search finds duplicates
body_html:
Searching for torch.nn.functional.conv2d returns results with 4 identical links to http://pytorch.org/docs/master/nn.html?highlight=torch%20nn%20functional%20conv2d#torch.nn.functional.conv2d

Link with results is: http://pytorch.org/docs/master/search.html?q=torch.nn.functional.conv2d&check_keywords=yes&area=default

This is true for master and 0.3
